docstring:
Parameter of a full order flux stator-rotor model without zero sequence flux in the stator.
 The derivative of stator fluxes (d and q) is NOT neglected. Only one q-axis damping circuit is considered. All parameters are in machine per unit.
 Refer to Chapter 3 of Power System Stability and Control by P. Kundur or Chapter 11 of Power System Dynamics: Stability and Control, by J. Machowski, J. Bialek and J. Bumby, for more details.
 Note that the models are somewhat different (but equivalent) due to the different Park Transformation used in both books.

fields.name: R
fields.comment: Resistance after EMF in machine per unit

fields.name: R_f
fields.comment: Field rotor winding resistance in per unit

fields.name: R_1d
fields.comment: Damping rotor winding resistance on d-axis in per unit. This value is denoted as RD in Machowski.

fields.name: R_1q
fields.comment: Damping rotor winding resistance on q-axis in per unit. This value is denoted as RQ in Machowski.

fields.name: L_d
fields.comment: Inductance of fictitious damping that represent the effect of the three-phase stator winding in the d-axis of the rotor, in per unit. This value is denoted as L_ad + L_l in Kundur (and Ld in Machowski).

fields.name: L_q
fields.comment: Inductance of fictitious damping that represent the effect of the three-phase stator winding in the q-axis of the rotor, in per unit. This value is denoted as L_aq + L_l in Kundur.

fields.name: L_ad
fields.comment: Mutual inductance between stator winding and rotor field (and damping) winding inductance on d-axis, in per unit

fields.name: L_aq
fields.comment: Mutual inductance between stator winding and rotor damping winding inductance on q-axis, in per unit

fields.name: L_f1d
fields.comment: Mutual inductance between rotor field winding and rotor damping winding inductance on d-axis, in per unit

fields.name: L_ff
fields.comment: Field rotor winding inductance, in per unit

fields.name: L_1d
fields.comment: Inductance of the d-axis rotor damping circuit, in per unit

fields.name: L_1q
fields.comment: Inductance of the q-axis rotor damping circuit, in per unit

fields.name: MVABase
fields.comment: Nominal Capacity in MVA

fields.name: inv_d_fluxlink
fields.internal_default: inv([[-L_d L_ad L_ad]; [-L_ad L_ff L_f1d]; [-L_ad L_f1d L_1d]])
fields.comment: Equations 3.127, 3.130, 3.131 From Kundur

fields.name: inv_q_fluxlink
fields.comment: Equations 3.128, 3.132 From Kundur

fields.name: internal
fields.comment: power system internal reference, do not modify
